[[Image:bigbarrel.gif|center|The Barrel full of Barrels]]

[[The Barrel full of Barrels]] is located in [[The Big Mountains]]. To adventure here, you need to complete the first task at your guild ([[The Brotherhood of the Smackdown]], [[The League of Chef-Magi]], [[The Department of Shadowy Arts and Crafts]]). When you enter, you'll be faced with 36 barrels -- 6 per row and column. Clicking on one smashes it, and takes one adventure. Either you'll find an item or fight a mimic, or the barrel will explode.  Each barrel can only be smashed once.  At rollover, all the barrels will be reset and randomized. The number of obstacles and the quality of awards increase in barrels closer to the top of the frame. This means that the top two rows are probably the rows to focus on. If you can defeat the mimics you will do well in these rows. The grid of barrels is subdivided into 9 2x2 sections ("quads").  Every barrel in a 2x2 section contains the same category of prize.  Within a row the 2x2 sections seem random, except there is always one of each of the three types and the pattern for one pair of rows (say Booze, Stats, Restore) is not repeated for any other pair of rows. Additionally, note that there are actually only nine arrangements of quads that ever show up; observed patterns from smashing in one quad can be used to calculate conditional probabilities to maximize the chances of grabbing the desired item class (see [[#Notes|Notes]]).
