==Notes==
*There are only nine observable arrangements of the quads. AFH has put together a [http://www.alliancefromhell.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=949 barrel probability tool] to assist barrel-smashers in their quest for booty. Summary of the nine distributions of ''B''ooze items, ''S''pleen items, and ''R''estoratives:
 BSR - BRS - RSB - SBR - BRS - RBS - SRB - BRS - RSB
 BRS - RSB - SBR - BRS - RBS - SRB - BRS - RSB - BSR
 RSB - SBR - BRS - RBS - SRB - BRS - RSB - BSR - BRS

*In the absence of any conditional data, of the nine possible quad arrangements, the top-row mixed booze is in the left quad in four cases, the middle in two cases, and the right in three.
*For unmixed booze in the middle row, four of nine arrangements are in the left, two in the middle, and three in the right.
*If you smash a barrel that you already smashed (by clicking twice in a row on the same barrel when the server's slow, or by using the "back" button), you get an error message saying:
:KOMPRESSOR does not smash (barrel #''N''.)<br>(You tried to smash a barrel which was already smashed. Perhaps you are clicking too many times on the barrel.)
*Until October 3, 2006, the "Your Barrel A Splode" text read:
:It explodes, hurting you.  Badly.
*Until October 11, 2005, the Barrel was a regular zone with unlimited combat and non-combat adventures.

